(44, 21, 36, 44, 7, 54, 54, 'Away with him', 'Mob Reactions to Stephen and Paul', 'Both passages emphasize the violent reactions of the crowd towards the speakers. In Acts 7:54, the people are described as gnashing their teeth, while in Acts 21:36, they cry out against Paul, indicating a similar hostility.', 'theme', 0.321, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
