(44, 21, 37, 42, 21, 15, 15, 'May I speak unto thee?', 'Connection of Speech and Wisdom', 'This connection highlights the theme of effective communication in challenging situations. In Acts, Paul seeks to speak, while in Luke, the promise of wisdom is given for speaking against adversaries.', 'theme', 0.314, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
